acc_ring - a test of GPU direct with OpenACC.
           CUDA, PGI compiler, and openmpi are required.

$ make
$ mpirun -x PSM2_GPUDIRECT=1 -x PSM2_CUDA=1 -x LD_LIBRARY_PATH -np 8 -npernode 4 ./a.out $((1024*1024)) 2>/dev/null
